def solve(arr):
    return [a for i,a in enumerate(arr) if all(x < a for x in arr[i+1:])]

def solve(arr):
    return [a for i,a in enumerate(arr) if a > max(arr[i+1:]+[0])]

def solve(arr):
    return [n for i,n in enumerate(arr) if all(n > x for x in arr[i + 1:])]

def solve(arr):
    return [n for i, n in enumerate(arr) if n > max(arr[i+1:], default=0)]

def solve(arr):
    return [a for i, a in enumerate(arr[:-1]) if a > max(arr[i+1:])] + [arr[-1]]
